NEC Decoder using GPIO and SysTick functionality of STM32C031C6.

The code assumes the connections provided in 'circuit.png'.

Final build binary of the firmware - "build/firmware.bin"

To build use: make all
To clean use: make clean

References:
https://www.st.com/resource/en/reference_manual/rm0490-stm32c0-series-advanced-armbased-32bit-mcus-stmicroelectronics.pdf

https://developer.arm.com/documentation/102835/0100/?lang=en

